--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
make | make all               Generates dependencies *.dep and object files.
                              Then links it into output file.
make clean                    Deletes all generated files, zip file
                              and documentation.

make zip                      Zips all code files (*.c, *.h, Makefile) into
                              .tar.gz archive.
make doc                      Generates Doxygen documentation into ./doc/.

make help                     Prints this help.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
